* Equation numbers must be explicitly enabled in the MathJax config as described in the [documentation](http://docs.mathjax.org/en/latest/options/input-processors/TeX.html). For example this is a config that works:

    ```html
    <script type="text/x-mathjax-config">
    MathJax.Hub.Config({
      config: ["MMLorHTML.js"],
      jax: ["input/TeX", "output/HTML-CSS", "output/NativeMML"],
      extensions: ["MathMenu.js", "MathZoom.js"],
      TeX: {
        equationNumbers: {autoNumber: "AMS"}
      }
    });
    </script>
    ```
* In the first line, you need to add the delimiters around `\eqref{eq:sample}`, like this: `\(\eqref{eq:sample}\)`.

